1. Moj *erik* je visok i mršav. (My Eric is tall and skinny.)
2. Želim da kupim novi *erić* za kuću. (I want to buy a new rug for the house.)
3. *Erića* često vidim u parku kako trči. (I often see Eric running in the park.)
4. Da li si video *erika* koji je juče bio na žurci? (Did you see the Eric who was at the party yesterday?)
5. Moja sestra ima mnogo igračaka, ali najdraži joj je plišani *erić*. (My sister has a lot of toys, but her favorite is a plush Eric.)
6. Na poslu imam mnogo obaveza, pa mi je *erić* za stres neophodan. (I have a lot of responsibilities at work, so a stress ball is essential for me.)
7. *Erićev* omiljeni film je "Pakleni šund". (Eric's favorite movie is "Pulp Fiction".)
8. Na pijaci sam kupila nekoliko *erića* crnog luka za dva dolara. (I bought a few pounds of onions for two dollars at the market.)
9. *Erićima* se odavno ne igram, jer su mi dosadili. (I haven't played with Erics in a long time because I'm bored of them.)
10. *Eriću* je potrebno da se malo smiri i da razmisli pre nego što nešto kaže. (Eric needs to calm down and think before he says something.)